  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IValidationRunListener
    An IValidationRunListener is notified when a validation is done
    IVolumeValidator
    An IVolumeValidator validates an input file(s) of a volume to be of appropriate format
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractXMLVolumeValidator
    AbstractXMLVolumeValidator provides functionality required by IVolumeValidators that validate XML format input
    ValidationRun
    ValidationRun can be passed to a thread to run an IVolumeValidator
